RapLeaf,allows,businesses,to,personalize,their,online,content,for,users,by,aggregating,public,information,available,online,and,data,from,offline,sources,The,Utilities,API,contains,tools,used,for,data,normalization,and,deduction,which,Rapleaf,uses,internally,in,their,data,processing,workflow,The,tools,include,returning,a,gender,based,on,a,name,deducing,a,name,from,an,email,address,or,username,and,normalizing,part,of,name,for,a,name,string,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON